author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
"The Good Life" is the latest single by Sleaford Mods featuring Gwendoline Christie & Big Special. It's taken from their upcoming album, The Demise of Planet X. I've been a fan of Sleaford Mods and vocalist Jason Williamson for a while now, so allow me to explain why in this review...
Technical side note:  I was testing my new 'mobile studio' during this episode, so apologies for the glitches with The Darkness..... . 

To watch The Good Life in its entirety - you can find it here: https://youtu.be/SyVICFIQlDg?si=e--I5Q0WuQIDs6qZ
The 'dark' version is here:  https://youtu.be/aaynJpIuaCY?si=dr98hHxp2aDMvh0C

To see Justin Hawkins Rides Again LIVE across the UK, you can find tickets here: 
https://www.aegpresents.co.uk/event/justin-hawkins-rides-again/

I'm currently on tour with The Darkness in the USA - you can find details here: 
https://www.thedarknesslive.com/tour-dates/

To see more from JHRA,  join my Patreon here: http://www.patreon.com/jushawk
